  <div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;" data-rte-preserve-empty="true">Your program includes expert led private training with Guy Codio and the New York Personal Training team, fully-customized to your goals. Whether you’re aiming for sculpted arms, a stronger back, improved posture, or full-body toning, every session is intentionally designed to help you look and feel your absolute best. We combine measurable progress tracking through data-driven metrics with ongoing accountability and expert guidance to help you achieve your ideal wedding-day physique.</p></div>


  
